libcotp
------------------------------------------
C library that generates TOTP and HOTP according to RFC-6238

Runtime requirements:
  cygwin-2.11.2-1
  libbaseencode1-1.0.9-1bl1
  libcotp-devel-1.2.1-1bl1
  libcotp12-1.2.1-1bl1
  libgcrypt20-1.8.2-1
  pkg-config-0.29.1-1

Build requirements:
(besides corresponding -devel packages)
  binutils-2.29-1
  cmake-3.6.2-1
  cygport-0.31.1-1
  gcc-core-7.3.0-3
  make-4.2.1-2
  ninja-1.8.2-2

Canonical website:
  https://github.com/paolostivanin/libcotp

Canonical download:
  https://github.com/paolostivanin/libcotp/archive/v1.2.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack libcotp-1.2.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./libcotp-1.2.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/libcotp-1.2.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcotp-1.2.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcotp12-1.2.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/libcotp-devel-1.2.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

Files included in the binary package:

(libcotp)
  /usr/share/doc/Cygwin/libcotp.README
  /usr/share/doc/libcotp/LICENSE
  /usr/share/doc/libcotp/README.md

(libcotp12)
  /usr/bin/cygcotp-12.dll

(libcotp-devel)
  /usr/include/cotp.h
  /usr/lib/libcotp.dll.a
  /usr/lib/pkgconfig/cotp.pc

